fields.description: The human-readable details of the conditional access session management policy applied to the sign-in.
fields.name: Detail

fields.description: If a conditional access session management policy required the user to authenticate in this sign-in event, this field describes the policy type that required authentication. The possible values are: rememberMultifactorAuthenticationOnTrustedDevices, tenantTokenLifetimePolicy, audienceTokenLifetimePolicy, signInFrequencyPeriodicReauthentication, ngcMfa, signInFrequencyEveryTime, unknownFutureValue.
